    <p>Our core values are a living document. We will continue to interview rural women to hear more about our lived experiences. If you would like to be interviewed, please email interviews@ruralfeminist.com.</p>
    <p>Input and edits on our existing core values are always welcome and encouraged. Please email corevalues@ruralfeminist.com.</p>
